sequenceDiagram
    participant Raj as Raj<br/>Galaxy S24
    participant HCE as Google Pay<br/>HCE Service
    participant Cloud as Google Cloud<br/>Pay Backend
    participant Terminal as PAX Terminal<br/>Bengaluru Shop
    participant Acquirer as Acquirer<br/>Processor
    participant Visa as VisaNet<br/>plus VTS
    participant HDFC as HDFC Bank<br/>Issuer

    Note over Raj,HDFC: Raj pays INR 1,200 at a shop in Bengaluru

    Note over HCE,Cloud: Pre-cached: batch of LUKs downloaded from cloud

    Raj->>HCE: Unlock phone, open Google Wallet
    HCE->>HCE: TEE verifies fingerprint<br/>via ARM TrustZone

    Raj->>Terminal: Taps phone on PAX terminal
    Terminal->>HCE: SELECT PPSE
    HCE-->>Terminal: Available AIDs -- Visa
    Terminal->>HCE: SELECT A0000000031010
    Terminal->>HCE: GET PROCESSING OPTIONS<br/>Amount: INR 1,200
    HCE->>HCE: Retrieve cached LUK<br/>Generate cryptogram<br/>Decrement LUK counter
    HCE-->>Terminal: DPAN plus LUK-based cryptogram

    Note over Raj,Terminal: NFC complete -- phone removed

    Terminal->>Acquirer: ISO 8583 0100 auth request
    Acquirer->>Visa: Route via token BIN
    Visa->>Visa: VTS detokenizes DPAN<br/>Validates LUK cryptogram<br/>using master key in vault
    Visa->>HDFC: Auth request with real PAN<br/>INR 1,200

    HDFC->>HDFC: Check debit account balance<br/>INR 1,200 available<br/>Fraud checks pass
    HDFC-->>Visa: Approved
    Visa-->>Acquirer: Re-tokenized response
    Acquirer-->>Terminal: Approved
    Terminal-->>Raj: Receipt printed

    Note over HCE,Cloud: If LUK batch running low
    HCE->>Cloud: Request fresh LUKs
    Cloud->>Cloud: Verify device attestation<br/>Play Integrity API check
    Cloud-->>HCE: New LUK batch downloaded
